      <title>DraftKings 因客户增长而上调年度销售预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/draftkings-raises-annual-sales-forecast-citing-customer-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[DraftKings Inc. 提高了年度销售和利润目标，尽管这家在线博彩巨头公布的一些第一季度业绩未达到分析师的预期。]]></description>
